{"type": "article", "id": 35563, "title": "再看一个幼儿园设计，它藏了很多玩乐小心思", "description": "简洁、温暖、不花哨", "date": "2016-12-14T05:15:43Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 272, "name": "建筑设计"}, {"id": 4187, "name": "幼儿园"}], "category": 17, "author": 699147, "comment_count": 5, "praise_count": 265, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161214005656DYp096Tbfth1jAVK.png", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000; min-height: 13.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>位于意大利北部博尔扎诺自治省的 Valdaora di Sotto，是个四面环山的安静小镇。有着深红色尖顶的教堂，是小镇中最醒目的建筑。其他房屋，基本都是粉饰一新的白墙搭配深色的屋瓦，高高低低地散落在乡间小道边。也有几栋年代稍久的房子，墙面用木板装饰，十分古朴。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161214125214ZvjXiESs93oFrDuh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.616549\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">小镇远景（来源：<a href=\"http://afasiaarchzine.com/2016/11/feld72-3/\" rel=\"nofollow\">afasiaarchzine</a>，摄影：Hertha Hurnaus）</figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161214125211qaHifJyAbrYRUMeO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.644275\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161214125213SgvpwoZU8Wns1bMY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.697387\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">小镇中的房子（谷歌地图截图）</figcaption></figure></div><p>就在教堂附近，一座新的幼儿园在今年建成。整体设计十分低调：一半的墙面被漆成白色，剩下的部分露出完整的长木条，和周围的小镇建筑以及自然景物，和谐相融。</p><p class=\"\">负责设计的是意大利的建筑设计事务所 feld 72，六年前他们曾在同省的 <a href=\"http://www.archdaily.com/93632/kindergarten-terenten-feld72\" rel=\"nofollow\">Terenten</a> 设计过另一座幼儿园，木制元素加白色墙体的设计，和这座新的幼儿园有些相似。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016121412544301GCNcBYr9kadnfX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.495215\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161214125443wAnL4ogUz3VWBXjI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664452\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161214125445DY7rmjvnutgJ2A5c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667035\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161214125446JImY4XqsA2BpDuhS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666298\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">幼儿园外观（来源：<a href=\"http://www.archdaily.com/801003/kindergarten-valdaora-di-sotto-feld72\" rel=\"nofollow\">archdaily</a>，摄影：Hertha Hurnaus）</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">整座幼儿园占地 950 平方米，一大半面积分给了露天庭院。庭院植上了草皮，中部还划出了一小块沙地，孩子们可以在里面堆沙子玩。靠近庭院的一侧墙体，是一片隐匿的小天地，里面有一面安装了木梯的攀岩墙，还有一部滑滑梯；即使在雨天，这块娱乐区加上能避雨的室外走廊，也可以让孩子们愉快地玩耍。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612141259470DWpGXb7ET6BS9dP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.668258\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161214125951xZ5qb8Bto6nir3e1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.670927\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161214125946i2U0v1AwNXSVpYyK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665193\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161214125950GqWv2D5nRkbruxN1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.504854\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161214125948Zof8PWjuDw7OG6Rl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.491647\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">室外的活动空间（来源：<a href=\"http://afasiaarchzine.com/2016/11/feld72-3/\" rel=\"nofollow\">afasiaarchzine</a>，摄影：Hertha Hurnaus）</figcaption></figure></div><p class=\"\">幼儿园的室内设计，从地板、墙面一直到天花板，全用暖色调的木板装饰，配上透进大落地窗的阳光，为整个空间营造了一种温暖舒适的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161214130108BF2inMvRzlfeqVuk.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665193\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161214130108PowHmEQMNVFJ9UZ2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666298\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">明亮温暖的室内空间（来源：<a href=\"http://afasiaarchzine.com/2016/11/feld72-3/\" rel=\"nofollow\">afasiaarchzine</a>，摄影：Hertha Hurnaus）</figcaption></figure></div><p>室内设计真正出彩的地方在于，绝大多数功能区的设置，都是为儿童量身定制的。比如沿走廊而设的小衣帽间，每一个孩子都有一块自己专属的存储区，他们可以自己动手将外套挂在挂钩上，把帽子、围巾等小件物品放到上方的长方形小柜中，还可以坐在长条木凳上换鞋，并将鞋子放置到长凳下方。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161214130238kSldsmCDVKGJQZL4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665871\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">衣帽间（来源：<a href=\"http://afasiaarchzine.com/2016/11/feld72-3/\" rel=\"nofollow\">afasiaarchzine</a>，摄影：Hertha Hurnaus）</figcaption></figure></div><p>用成人的眼光去看，这片专属于儿童的天地，充满了萌感。他们有自己的茶水间和储物柜，在窗台边，还有一块小休息区，可以坐在台阶或靠着枕头看书。而在室内的各个角落，都有可以玩耍的区域：孩子们可以自由地在台阶上爬上爬下，从木制滑梯上滑下来，还可以藏进楼梯下方玩个捉迷藏。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161214130310rGw2H7doBYM53TO6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667461\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161214130312o0bFmdhvXUj4k8S3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665871\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161214130314s6ZPr4eY28gQ5FH9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667995\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161214130311yx7YCkrRZ6TAzfbK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612141303126NZmfAVE12tlGLrW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.496403\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161214130310ckanO1ND8KtgELsZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.248000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\">充满童趣的设计（来源：<a href=\"http://afasiaarchzine.com/2016/11/feld72-3/\" rel=\"nofollow\">afasiaarchzine</a>，摄影：Hertha Hurnaus）</figcaption></figure></div><p>这个项目能最终在当地政府组织的设计竞赛中胜出，或许和这种尽力让孩子们释放天性的设计理念，不无关系。</p><p><br></p><p class=\"\">题图：<a href=\"http://www.archdaily.com/801003/kindergarten-valdaora-di-sotto-feld72\" rel=\"nofollow\">archdaily</a>，Hertha Hurnaus</p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; font: 11.0px Helvetica; -webkit-text-stroke: #000000} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p>"}